{"name": "morefs", "metadata": {"name": "morefs", "version": "0.2.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": "Apache-2.0", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["fsspec"], "summary": "A collection of self-contained fsspec-based filesystems", "upload_time": 1720411816}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  Black: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg\n    :alt: Black\n    :target: https://github.com/psf/black\n    ```\n  Codecov: |-\n    ```{image} https://codecov.io/gh/iterative/morefs/branch/main/graph/badge.svg\n    :alt: Codecov\n    :target: https://app.codecov.io/gh/iterative/morefs\n    ```\n  License: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/morefs\n    :alt: License\n    :target: https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0\n    ```\n  PyPI: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/morefs.svg\n    :alt: PyPI\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/morefs/\n    ```\n  Python Version: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/morefs\n    :alt: Python Version\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/morefs\n    ```\n  Status: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/status/morefs.svg\n    :alt: Status\n    :target: https://pypi.org/project/morefs/\n    ```\n  Tests: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/iterative/morefs/workflows/Tests/badge.svg\n    :alt: Tests\n    :target: https://github.com/iterative/morefs/actions?workflow=Tests\n    ```\n  pre-commit: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/pre--commit-enabled-brightgreen?logo=pre-commit&logoColor=white\n    :alt: pre-commit\n    :target: https://github.com/pre-commit/pre-commit\n    ```\n---\n\n# morefs\n\n{{ PyPI }} {{ Status }} {{ Python Version }} {{ License }}\n\n{{ Tests }} {{ Codecov }} {{ pre-commit }} {{ Black }}\n\n## Features\n\n*morefs* provides standalone fsspec-based filesystems like:\n\n- `AsyncLocalFileSystem` that provides async implementation of `LocalFileSystem`.\n- In-memory filesystems `DictFileSystem` built on nested dictionaries and `MemFS` built on tries, and are much faster than fsspec's `MemoryFileSystem`.\n- `OverlayFileSystem` that allows to overlay multiple fsspec-based filesystems.\n\n## Installation\n\nYou can install *morefs* via [pip] from [PyPI]:\n\n```console\n$ pip install morefs\n```\n\nYou might need to install with extras for some filesystems:\n\n```console\n$ pip install morefs[asynclocal]  # for installing aiofile dependency for AsyncLocalFileSystem\n$ pip install morefs[memfs]  # for installing pygtrie dependency for MemFS\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n### AsyncLocalFileSystem\n\nExtended version of `LocalFileSystem` that also provides async methods.\n\n```python\nimport asyncio\nfrom morefs.asyn_local import AsyncLocalFileSystem\n\nasync def main():\n    fs = AsyncLocalFileSystem(auto_mkdir=False)\n\n    f = await fs.open_async(\"foo\", mode=\"w\")\n    async with f:\n        await f.write(\"foobar\")\n\n    content = await fs._cat(\"foo\")\n    print(content)\n    print(fs.cat(\"foo\"))  # you can still use sync methods\n\nasyncio.run(main())\n```\n\n### DictFS\n\nDictFS is a nested dictionary-based, in-memory filesystem\nand acts more like a real LocalFileSystem.\n\n```python\nfrom morefs.dict import filesystem\n\nfs = DictFS()\n```\n\n### MemFS\n\nMemFS is a trie-based in-memory filesystem, and acts like a bucket storage.\n\n```python\nfrom morefs.memory import MemFS\n\nfs = MemFS()\n```\n\n### OverlayFileSystem\n\n```python\nfrom morefs.overlay import OverlayFileSystem\n\n# use localfilesystem for write, overlay all filesystems for read\nfs = OverlayFileSystem(file={\"auto_mkdir\": True}, s3={\"anon\": True})\n# or you can pass filesystem instances directly\n# as variable positional arguments or with keyword argument `filesystems=[]`\nfs = OverlayFileSystem(LocalFileSystem(), s3={\"anon\": True})\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\nContributions are very welcome.\nTo learn more, see the [Contributor Guide].\n\n## License\n\nDistributed under the terms of the [Apache 2.0 license],\n*morefs* is free and open source software.\n\n## Issues\n\nIf you encounter any problems,\nplease [file an issue] along with a detailed description.\n\n% github-only\n\n[apache 2.0 license]: https://opensource.org/licenses/Apache-2.0\n[contributor guide]: CONTRIBUTING.rst\n[file an issue]: https://github.com/iterative/morefs/issues\n[pip]: https://pip.pypa.io/\n[pypi]: https://pypi.org/\n"], "modules": [{"name": "morefs.asyn_local", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "morefs.asyn_local.wrap", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "func", "type": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "P", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "R", "xref": {"fqname": "R", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "P", "xref": null, "params": null}, {"name": "Awaitable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Awaitable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "R", "xref": {"fqname": "R", "project": null}, "params": null}]}]}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "morefs.asyn_local.P", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "morefs.asyn_local.R", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "morefs.asyn_local.AsyncLocalFileSystem", "bases": ["AsyncFileSystem", "LocalFileSystem"], "methods": [{"name": "morefs.asyn_local.AsyncLocalFileSystem._get_file", "asynchronous": true, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "src", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "dst", "type": nul